  <name>qeth</name>
  <summary>Qt Ethereum wallet with Ledger support</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      qeth is a Qt-based Ethereum desktop wallet with Ledger hardware-wallet
      support and a Frame-compatible JSON-RPC server, so dapps in the browser
      can connect to it unchanged.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Ledger and watch-only accounts, plus encrypted hot wallets</li>
      <li>Token discovery and balances across Ethereum, OP, Polygon, Arbitrum and Base</li>
      <li>Send native and ERC-20 assets, with ENS-name resolution and an address book</li>
      <li>Speed up or cancel pending transactions (replace-by-fee)</li>
      <li>Contract-identity hints: who deployed it, and how often you've interacted</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.michwill.qeth.desktop</launchable>
